
### Conversion
samtools view -C -T /scratch/project_2000886/Elisa/reseq/GCA_024166365.1_mEleMax1_primary_haplotype_genomic.fa \
  -o SAMPLENAME_sorted_duplicates_reads.cram \
  SAMPLENAME_sorted_duplicates_reads.bam

### Indexation
samtools index SAMPLENAME_sorted_duplicates_reads.cram

### Verification
samtools quickcheck SAMPLENAME_sorted_duplicates_reads.cram

### Flagstat
samtools flagstat SAMPLENAME_sorted_duplicates_reads.cram > SAMPLENAME_sorted_duplicates_reads.flagstat.cram.txt


